Huge menu of sandwiches, entrees, salads and an all vegan dessert case!

My friend and I got chicken seitan cheeseburger and a chicken sandwich with avocado, which were both delicious. We also got an amazing chocolate cake! The chocolate cake’s middle layer was a chocolate frosting with crispy crumbled crepe and a chocolate raspberry frosting on top.

photos: http://vegansinspain.wordpress.com/2010/07/24/july-24-love-love-loving-barcelona/
